import React from "react";
import { Container, Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap";
import Navigation from "../Component/Navigation";
import "./Style.css";
import { FaFacebookSquare } from "react-icons/fa";
import { BsInstagram, BsTwitter, BsLinkedin, BsGithub } from "react-icons/bs";

const About = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Row>
        <Navigation />
      </Row>
      <Row>
          <Container>
        <Col className="about-background mt-5">
          <Row> Name - Aatish</Row>
          <Row>Contact Us:</Row>
          <Row>
            <Col>
              <FaFacebookSquare />
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <BsInstagram />
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <BsTwitter />
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <BsLinkedin />
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <BsGithub />
            </Col>
          </Row>
        </Col>
        <Col className="about-background-ritu mt-5 ml-5">
          <Row> Name - Ritu Kumari</Row>
          <Row>Contact Us:</Row>
          <Row>
            <Col>
              <FaFacebookSquare />
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <BsInstagram />
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <BsTwitter />
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <BsLinkedin />
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <BsGithub />
            </Col>
          </Row>
        </Col>
        </Container>
      </Row>
    </>
  );
};
export default About;
